GREENLAND-SOUTHWEST COAST.
16 FOOT VESSEL, TWO PERSONS ON BOARD, WHITE HULL,
DISABLED AND ADRIFT DUE TO ENGINE DAMAGE,
UNREPORTED NUUK (64-10-30N 051-44-20W) TO
NAPASOQ (65-02-50N 052-22-50W). LAST KNOWN
POSITION ATAMMIK (64-48-13N 052-10-35W).
VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED TO KEEP
A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE.
REPORTS TO AASIAAT RADIO.
